title: Jessi's Story
description:
In this episode, Jessi talks about her journey to salon ownership and experiences that shaped who she is today. JZ Styles started 4 years ago and it's in a completely different place now than when it started. Hear about the up's and down's as she explains the last 4 years and how she started it all.
